data.description: Discover the perfect blend of modern living and convenience in this meticulously maintained 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in Leisurewoods. With a generous 2,222 square feet of living space, this home is situated on a large, flat, and private lot that spans over half an acre. Ideally positioned for easy access to downtown via Highway 45 and Mopac. This home is the epitome of modern comfort and convenience. Recent upgrades, including new HVAC, septic system, updated kitchen & bathrooms, make it move-in ready. Inside, the elegant touches such as crown molding, neutral color pallet, upgraded finishes and luxury vinyl plank floors add a touch of sophistication. The layout offers flexibility with bonus rooms for your personal use. This home is perfect for entertaining downstairs and relaxation upstairs. The bedrooms are all very spacious with plenty of storage. Outside, the expansive backyard provides ample space and privacy for your outdoor enjoyment. Seize this opportunity to own a beautifully updated home in a highly desirable neighborhood of Leisurewood. Take advantage of the spacious lot and recent upgrades, and experience all the benefits of this fantastic location. Schedule your viewing today and make this house your home! Don't miss this amazing opportunity of an assumable mortgage at 2.5%.
